    <item>
      <title>美联储降息势将撼动市场，Pimco 和 GMO 完善新兴市场策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/pimco-gmo-refine-em-playbook-as-fed-cuts-set-to-shake-up-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国几十年来最令人期待的降息为今年遭受近 150 亿美元资金流出的资产类别带来了新的动力，表现最佳的新兴市场债券经理正在重新调整头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/pimco-gmo-refine-em-playbook-as-fed-cuts-set-to-shake-up-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普最新的加密货币投资体现了家人的全心全意拥抱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-trump-crypto-endeavor-exemplifies-wholehearted-embrace-by-family</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普现在倡导去中心化金融平台，并承诺将美国打造为世界的“加密之都”，所有人的目光都集中在这位前总统的家人和同事日益壮大的数字资产努力上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/latest-trump-crypto-endeavor-exemplifies-wholehearted-embrace-by-family</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡派助手前往莫斯科寻求解决加沙人质问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/netanyahu-sent-aide-to-moscow-seeking-progress-on-gaza-hostages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示，以色列寻求俄罗斯的帮助，以推动达成释放加沙人质的协议，而美国、卡塔尔和埃及牵头的与哈马斯停火的努力进展缓慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/netanyahu-sent-aide-to-moscow-seeking-progress-on-gaza-hostages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>集装箱运输公司利润因货运量创纪录和运价上涨而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/container-carrier-profits-soar-on-record-volumes-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新分析显示，由于红海改道后货运量创纪录且运费上涨，全球集装箱航运业第二季度利润飙升至 100 亿美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/container-carrier-profits-soar-on-record-volumes-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
