    <item>
      <title>捷克提议在 2025 年选举年遏制预算赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克财政部提出了一项在 2025 年选举年削减预算赤字的计划，此举引发了执政联盟关于支出优先事项的争论，因为执政党正努力应对日益增长的公众不满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国努力结束危机，利比亚石油产量仍面临不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/libya-s-agoco-to-restart-production-amid-central-bank-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚的确切石油产量充满不确定性，尽管由于欧佩克成员国政府之间的争执，一个主要油田的产量进一步削减，但该国三个油田仍被要求逐步恢复抽油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/libya-s-agoco-to-restart-production-amid-central-bank-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 21:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
